# Lowercase UI Text

All visible UI text in the prototype must be fully lowercase — section titles, labels, buttons, headings, badges, etc. Never use title case, sentence case, or uppercase for any user-facing string.

```tsx
// bad
<CollectionSection title="Popular Items in Hennepin Co" />

// good
<CollectionSection title="popular items in hennepin co" />
```
